beer.beer_description: This ravishing Brown Ale was brewed in collaboration with Sydney’s Brix Rum Distillers. It’s solid malt bill creates a rich, roasty, biscuity flavour and aroma with hints of cocoa and spice, leading to the showcase of a classic partnership... Aussie Raisins steeped in Brix White Spirit. This very adult beverage will hopefully dredge up memories of that childhood ice cream classic and is best enjoyed with old friends, family and a block of dark chocolate.
